<subSubSection id="C31F78D00C1D8D69FF0FFDFDFC796FE5" pageId="9" pageNumber="174" type="biology_ecology">
<paragraph id="8BBA2B5B0C1D8D69FF0FFDFDFC796FE5" blockId="9.[151,1437,151,861]" pageId="9" pageNumber="174">
<emphasis id="B971F7490C1D8D69FF0FFDFDFE7F6F15" bold="true" box="[199,503,548,573]" pageId="9" pageNumber="174">Biology and distribution.</emphasis>
<taxonomicName id="4C0550D80C1D8D69FDC9FDFDFD5E6F14" authorityName="Freitas" authorityYear="2017" baseAuthorityName="P. Jauffret, J. Jauffret &amp; Pessoa" baseAuthorityYear="2008" box="[513,726,548,572]" class="Insecta" family="Riodinidae" genus="Sertania" kingdom="Animalia" order="Lepidoptera" pageId="9" pageNumber="174" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="lambedor">
<emphasis id="B971F7490C1D8D69FDC9FDFDFD5E6F14" box="[513,726,548,572]" italics="true" pageId="9" pageNumber="174">Sertania lambedor</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
was observed flying rapidly about a meter above the ground along a dry stream bed in the caatinga. Adults landed on small flowers for short periods of time, being difficult to approach, thus making capture difficult (
<bibRefCitation id="EF9456AA0C1D8D69FD94FDB5FCBD6FAC" author="Jauffret" box="[604,821,620,645]" pageId="9" pageNumber="174" refString="Jauffret, P., Jauffret, J. C. &amp; Pessoa, A. (2008) Etudes preliminaires sur la faune des Riodinidae du nord-est bresilien - Etat du Ceara. (Lepidoptera). Description d'une espece et de trois sous especes nouvelles (9 eme note). Lambillionea, CVIII (4), 501 - 510." type="journal article" year="2008">
Jauffret 
<emphasis id="B971F7490C1D8D69FD71FDB4FD626FAC" box="[697,746,620,644]" italics="true" pageId="9" pageNumber="174">et al</emphasis>
. 2008
</bibRefCitation>
). This species was recorded in six localities of caatinga (
<figureCitation id="133E37DE0C1D8D69FF57FD56FF7B6F80" box="[159,243,655,680]" captionStart="FIGURES 34 – 37" captionStartId="10.[151,264,1200,1222]" captionTargetBox="[151,1435,194,1179]" captionTargetId="figure@10.[151,1435,193,1179]" captionTargetPageId="10" captionText="FIGURES 34 – 37. Overview of Sertania gen. nov. habitats in South American ‘ dry diagonal’. 34 – 35, Sertania guttata comb. nov., monte vegetation (34) in Anillaco, La Rioja, and Chaco serrano (35) in Capilla del Monte, Cordoba, Argentina; 36, Sertania jaibensis comb. nov., stat. nov., rocky montane fields in Sempre Vivas National Park, Buenópolis, Minas Gerais, Brazil; 37, Sertania lambedor comb. nov., stat. nov., arboreal caatinga in Custódia, Pernambuco, Brazil. Photos (36) by CA Iserhard and (37) by DHA Melo." httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/892889/files/figure.png" pageId="9" pageNumber="174">Fig. 37</figureCitation>
) in northeast 
<collectingCountry id="F3126BCB0C1D8D69FE5BFD56FE526F80" box="[403,474,655,680]" name="Brazil" pageId="9" pageNumber="174">Brazil</collectingCountry>
, including the Parque Nacional do Catimbau, 
<collectingRegion id="49C1E5B90C1D8D69FC26FD56FBF56F80" box="[1006,1149,655,680]" country="Brazil" name="Pernambuco" pageId="9" pageNumber="174">Pernambuco</collectingRegion>
, and Parque Nacional da Serra das Confusões, 
<collectingRegion id="49C1E5B90C1D8D69FE41FD6DFE4B6FE5" box="[393,451,692,717]" country="Brazil" name="Piaui" pageId="9" pageNumber="174">Piaui</collectingRegion>
(
<bibRefCitation id="EF9456AA0C1D8D69FE19FD6DFD286FE4" author="Kerpel" box="[465,672,692,717]" pageId="9" pageNumber="174" refString="Kerpel, S. M., Zacca, T., Nobre, C. E. B., Ferreira-Jr., A., Araujo, M. X. &amp; Fonseca, A. (2014) Borboletas do Semiarido: conhecimento atual e contribuicoes do PPBio. In: Bravo, F. &amp; Calor, A. L. (Eds.), Artropodes do Semiarido: biodiversidade e conservacao. Printmidia, Feira de Santana, BA, Brazil, pp. 245 - 272." type="book chapter" year="2014">
Kerpel 
<emphasis id="B971F7490C1D8D69FDEEFD6CFDD06FE4" box="[550,600,692,716]" italics="true" pageId="9" pageNumber="174">et al</emphasis>
. 2014
</bibRefCitation>
, 
<bibRefCitation id="EF9456AA0C1D8D69FD64FD6DFC6D6FE5" author="Nobre" box="[684,997,692,717]" pageId="9" pageNumber="174" refString="Nobre, C. E. B. &amp; Schlindwein, C. (2016) Borboletas no Uale do Catimbau: guia de especies e flores visitadas. Verbis editora, Brasilia, 280 pp." type="book" year="2016">Nobre &amp; Schlindwein 2016</bibRefCitation>
).
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
